cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with optimization of models for legged locomotion, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of algorithms for optimization (cs.SY) and machine learning techniques for synthesizing models (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves analysis of locomotion patterns, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
